==Misc.==

This project is meant to provide a good basis for a wordpress theme, and was tested on version 4.9.5.

Things should '''mostly''' work right, but there may be things missing, so the theme is not exactly complete.

You can use this a theme, or to make a semidescent starting point for a theme of your own.